relation: Configures the access list mechanism for filtering frames by protocol type or vendor code.
Enables the router to send SNMP notification messages to a designated network management workstation.
Specifies the targeted recipient of an SNMP notification operation.
Creates or updates a view entry.

Usage Guidelines The Cisco MIB provides a chassis MIB variable that enables the SNMP manager to gather data on system card descriptions, chassis type, chassis hardware version, chassis ID string, software version of ROM monitor, software version of system image in ROM, bytes of processor RAM
